comments.body:
I think you can just replace this:
{code:java}
        String value = props.getProperty(name);
{code}
with this:
{code:java}
        String value = get(name);
{code}
I'm not certain if we need to worry about the deprecation stuff in Configuration.get() for this. If it's not needed, then I think this would be all we'd need:
{code:java}
        String value = substituteVars(props.getProperty(name));
{code}
